        "zh": "為何需要進行研究  <br>研究興趣與主題的探索<br>文獻的選擇與評論<br>設定合適的研究提問<br><br>",
        "en": "Why Research is Needed<br>Exploring Research Interests and Topics<br>Selection and Review of Literature<br>Setting Appropriate Research Questions<br>"
